---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us">
  <section class="section page-header">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Us</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Our story, purpose, and community values.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-wrapper">
        <h2>Our Story</h2>
        <p><strong>Friends of Baanaadi</strong> is a diverse community of birdwatching enthusiasts from various professional backgrounds, united by a shared passion for nature, wildlife, and avian life.</p>
        <p>Founded in December 2024, our community has been actively exploring, documenting, and appreciating the rich bird habitats in and around Bengaluru and its neighboring districts.</p>

        <h2>Our Purpose & Philosophy</h2>
        <p>We believe that birdwatching and nature exploration are powerful pathways to mindfulness, conservation, and lifelong learning. Our mission is to encourage outdoor activities, fostering birdwatching as a rewarding and accessible hobby for everyone.</p>
        <p>For us, observation and conservation go hand in hand. We are dedicated to contributing to scientific research and local biodiversity awareness by actively participating in citizen science initiatives, such as the annual Asian Waterbird Census (AWC), the Great Backyard Bird Count (GBBC), and year-round eBird documentation.</p>

        <h2>Our Community Values</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Inclusive to All:</strong> We warmly welcome participants of all ages, skill levels, and backgrounds. All that is required is curiosity and an appreciation for the natural world.</li>
          <li><strong>Experience Over Equipment:</strong> We are a birdwatching community, not a photography club. While photographers are welcome, our emphasis is on observing birds in their natural behaviors and soaking in the environment. We prefer active exploration and record-keeping (such as eBird checklists) over spending long hours waiting in one spot for a single, perfect photograph.</li>
          <li><strong>Consistent Engagement:</strong> To keep our community active, we conduct regular monthly outings and organize immersive nature stays and learning workshops twice a year.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    background-color: var(--color-surface);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    padding-top: var(--space-3xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--color-accent-primary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .section {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .content-wrapper h2 {
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }

  .content-wrapper h2:first-child {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .content-wrapper p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .content-wrapper ul {
    list-style-type: disc;
    padding-left: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .content-wrapper li {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .content-wrapper li strong {
    color: var(--color-text-primary);
  }
</style>
